OK, looks like the following construct sets up infinite computation loop in TensorFlow
```

@function.Defun(...)
def B:
  _symbolic_gradient(input=..., f="A")

@function.Defun(..., func_name="A", grad_func=B)
def A:
  ...

sess.run(tf.gradients(A(x), [x]), ...
```

